yder n\u00e5r forfatteren i sluttsatsen, Nye avskjedsritualer. Prosadiktet \u00abOppslagsord: kjole\u00bb er blant de vakreste jeg har lest"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "kultur|bok"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "kultur|bok|bokanmeldelser"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "6f909aae71ebed0bc9f0945826b03b19c89da4898f72e1eaeff2b549171e4c62"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-10-05T08:45:23.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "\u00c5 lese Cecilie L\u00f8veids dikt, er en sanseopplevelse for hele kroppen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/8b27a30b58bf42022073ef8ef09f27f5f50cb95c.jpg?59517652"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Sanselige dikt -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "8b27a30b58bf42022073ef8ef09f27f5f50cb95c"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "Literature"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Literature"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["bokanmeldelser", "kultur", "bok"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["dikt", "boken"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["bergensminne", "oppslagsord"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["trondheim", "norge", "bergen", "k\u00f8benhavn"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["cecilie l\u00f8veid", "georg johannesen"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["kultur/bok", "kultur", "kultur/bok/bokanmeldelser"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Sanselige dikt"}, {"field": "og-type", "value": "article"}, {"